owners.name: Tiana Robinson
owners.description: I'm just trying to have as many poodles as I possibly can! Cleo is my clone in dog form.

owners.name: Zach Rourke
owners.description: Et repellendus consequatur deserunt placeat amet impedit eaque harum.

owners.name: Maeghan Phan
owners.description: Penny and I like long walks on the beach, strolls through the dog park, and playing fetch! We keep it pretty laid back around here. Penny plays well with other dachshunds and dogs her own size. We're excited to find her some new doggie friends!

owners.name: Nick Valdez
owners.description: My wife and I live in Nashville where I play drums and she’s a social worker and we just gave birth to baby boy named Rio. Moose’s keeps our household active and out of the house!

dogs.name: Cleo
dogs.description: Long legged, some would say I’m like a baby giraffe but with extra floof. Like long walks on the beach and to be told I’m a pretty girl.

dogs.name: Aurora
dogs.description: Known to tackle a few toddlers and have chased some squirrels in my day, but I swear I'm a gentle giant. People are intimated by my wolfly demeanor, but I mean no trouble. Big fan of naps.

dogs.name: Moose
dogs.description: I love to be outdoors and prefer sticks and dirt to chew toys and anything else out of a package. I protec my lil bro Rio 4ever. I’m a stray wolf at heart, are you going to be the one who domesticates me?

dogs.name: Rio
dogs.description: I have my own personal bodyguard named Moose. Don't tell my parents I'm on here... I know I'm but a tiny human, but I need more dogs in my life.

dogs.name: George
dogs.description: I’m George! I’m a bit of a crazy boy but a total lover. I spend my time with my favorite hoomans and snuggling... lots of snuggling. I like going on adventures and sometimes enjoy yoga. My ideal first date would be an adventure at the dog park then get ice-cream. I am looking for my adventure partner. Will you be my sweetheart?

dogs.name: Gatsby
dogs.description: My ears look like Dobby. I was just born that way. I LOVE to bark, especially at squirrels. Squeaky toys are pretty much the best. Other dogs are fine; I'm pretty chill and get along with almost anyone. When I get nervous, I suck my thigh. I'm not a big fan of car rides but I am used to going to public places with my mom.

dogs.name: Penny
dogs.description: I LOVE people and sometimes like dogs. I've been told on numerous occasions I am literally the cutest thing someone has ever seen. I will sleep in your bed and snuggle up! I prefer to play at dog parks, off leash, or on my own turf. I will bark at you when I see you on a leash. Like, you probably want to stay away... I don't like to talk when I'm on a leash. I'm better with dogs my own size. I tolerate the existence of cats but only b/c I have to.

dogs.name: Bruno
dogs.description: I’m only 9 months old, but I’m already a chonkin 110 lbs. Still very clumsy, so I might break your fancy china with the swoosh of my bushy tail. I have two guinea pig brothers names Hank and Taro, and I could just sit and watch them all day long.
